{"product_id":"berrichi-face-oil-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Face Oil 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003ePure Vital Glow is a fast-absorbing face oil that replenishes skin moisture, strengthens the protective barrier, and brings out a natural glow. Astaxanthin provides powerful antioxidant defense, while bakuchiol supports cell renewal and a smoother, more even texture. A nourishing blend of oils improves elasticity and softness, keeping skin balanced and comfortable. The gentle scent of red mandarin turns skincare into a delightful ritual.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e – an exceptionally strong natural antioxidant (up to 6000× stronger than vitamin C), helps protect against UV exposure and free radicals, supports youthful-looking skin, and helps preserve collagen and elastin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBakuchiol oil\u003c\/span\u003e – a plant-based alternative to retinol that supports cell renewal, refines skin texture, and evens tone without the potential irritation of traditional retinol.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e – a natural source of retinol and vitamin E, helps smooth the skin’s surface, improves elasticity, and supports anti-age care.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRosehip seed oil\u003c\/span\u003e – rich in vitamin C, helps even out the complexion, supports collagen production, and improves elasticity.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBlack cumin seed oil\u003c\/span\u003e – calming and restorative, supports the skin’s barrier and suits mildly irritated skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eEvening primrose oil\u003c\/span\u003e – a source of gamma-linolenic acid (GLA), helps maintain moisture, softness, and comfort, especially for dry or sensitive skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMilk thistle oil\u003c\/span\u003e – rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, supports the skin’s natural defenses and helps reduce oxidative stress.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRed mandarin essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e – lends a gently citrus, feel-good aroma and makes skincare a pleasurable ritual.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin morning and evening before your cream, or mix a few drops of oil into your favorite moisturizer. Also perfect for facial massage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Simmondsia Chinensis Seed (Jojoba) Oil*, Nigella Sativa Seed (Black Cumin) Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel (Apricot) Oil*, Sambucus Nigra Seed (Elderberry) Oil*, Caryodendron Orinocense Seed (Cacay) Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil*, Silybum Marianum Seed (Milk Thistle) Oil*, Rosa Canina Seed (Rosehip) Extract*, Oenothera Biennis (Evening Primrose) Oil*, Ricinus Communis Seed (Castor) Oil*, Psoralea Corylifolia Seed (Bakuchi) Oil, Citrus Nobilis Peel (Mandarin) Oil Expressed,  Astaxanthin, Haematococcus Pluvialis Oil Tocopherol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified by Ecocert Greenlife according to COSMOS Standard\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53357252444487,"sku":null,"price":41.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-face-oil-30ml-4740726.png?v=1771546571","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-face-oil-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}